{
  "stem": "22869.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was saying at one time or another oh God, help me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the last thing in the world you had on your mind was the concept of thinking oh, maybe today is Sabbath, and I'm not supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was so far away from your mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think, at least in the stage that I was, that I had lost the whole concept or the whole way of thinking of wait a minute, you didn't pray today.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't-- it was completely lost.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because my main subconscious way of maybe one day going out from this calamity was what am I doing next?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe not in these terms as I'm expressing them now, but that was all I was geared-- my body was geared to.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How do I find something to take in my mouth to sustain myself?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do I escape and get in a place of work that I don't have to work so hard, where I can rest a little bit more?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, everything was geared towards sustaining oneself and to see yet the evening or tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, in this stage where we are arriving now to talk about, I would say was one of the lowest points of the 37 months that I suffered.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except later on in the end, as we will discuss later, that you saw people around you where you realized, from now on you are in hell.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You will never get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You saw people around you that had no more flesh left on their bodies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You saw people, when you looked at them, all you saw was skeletons.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
